CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 17, 1953, pg. 27, reads: "Fisherman's Dream - James Pressley, inventor of the 'Sure Catch' fishing instrument, is pictured above with his unique device. There's a good chance that Pressley's invention will be made available to the general public soon. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of James Pressley with cigar in mouth, squatting in alley with two fishing poles, tackle box, and his "Sure Catch" fishing instrument
